(Send safety + wallet behavior) Tj
T*
(- GUI send flow uses per-submit intent_id to avoid duplicate payment creation on retries.) Tj
T*
(- intent_in_progress responses are polled until completion.) Tj
T*
(- Wallet balances use balance_batch first, then fallback per-row calls when needed.) Tj
T*
(- Local tx history writes are debounced \(ATHO_GUI_HISTORY_WRITE_DEBOUNCE_SEC\) and flushed at) Tj
